race.description: Greyhounds As Pets Stake Pr2 Division3
race.comment: BROTHER BILO (4) is progressing well and looks close to another win after hitting the frame last run (22.60) at Gawler. Form at the trip excellent including two wins. Didn't win last time but still ran one of the quickest times on the card. One of the leading chances. ALLINGA ALAN (1) has been settling off the speed lately, finishing fifth (20.01) last time in a Grade 5 at this track. Solid record here winning five races. Goes very well from this draw with four wins and five minor placings from 10 starts. One of the main contenders. ICE AGE (5) has a strong record this trip including two wins from four starts. Was out of placings last time (26.06) at Murray Bridge in a Special conditions race, finishing fourth and beaten 8 lengths. Among the main chances. WEBLEC BLOSSOM (2) won last start in the fastest time on the card. Big chance on that form. Something for the Multiples: PALACE PRINCE (7)
